<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">This book takes a bit of time before you are really immersed into the plot before things make sense. It is worth sticking with it. It all makes sense,<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">This book takes a bit of time before you are really immersed into the plot before things make sense. It is worth sticking with it. It all makes sense, even if the concept of "leaving oneself" is not a reality you can comprehend. I was disappointed when it was over because I was captured by the story. A satisfying read. <a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
