<div id="review_310537824" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/310537824" />
    <a title="Nicholas Sparks" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/8721294-nicholas-sparks"><img alt="Nicholas Sparks" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1632811728p2/8721294.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/310537824?book_show_action=true">Apr 11, 2012</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Nicholas Sparks" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Nicholas Sparks" href="/user/show/8721294-nicholas-sparks">Nicholas Sparks</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/8721294-nicholas-sparks?shelf=nicholas-recommends">nicholas-recommends</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer310537824" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer11276939584806615033">It&apos;s a &quot;love story&quot; done &quot;Stephen King&quot; style and so perfectly done that my first thought after finishing was to read the novel a second time. The characters are so genuine and universal that everyone will love them, and the story is both magical and heart-breaking at exactly the same time. </span>
  <span id="freeText11276939584806615033" style="display:none">It's a "love story" done "Stephen King" style and so perfectly done that my first thought after finishing was to read the novel a second time. The characters are so genuine and universal that everyone will love them, and the story is both magical and heart-breaking at exactly the same time. </span>
  <a data-text-id="11276939584806615033" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


